{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-verb}}\n\n# {{lb|fr|transitive}} to [[wait]] for, to [[await]]\n#: {{uxi|fr|Je l''''attends'''.|I'm waiting for her/him.}}\n#: {{ux|fr|On '''attend''' le beau temps pour partir.|t=We're '''waiting''' for good weather to head out.}}\n#: {{ux|fr|J’'''attends''' mon cousin à la gare.|I''''m waiting''' for my cousin at the station.}}\n#* {{quote-book|fr|title=Le mariage du Naïf|author={{w|Paul Guth}}|year=1957|publisher=Le Livre de Poche|page=44|text=J’adore '''attendre'''. Ce sont les seuls moments de la vie où je me repose. Parfois je vais chez le coiffeur quand je n’en ai pas besoin, uniquement pour avoir le plaisir d’'''attendre'''.|t=I love '''waiting'''. It's the only moment in life where I relax. Sometimes I go to the hairdresser's even when I don't need to, solely to have the pleasure of '''waiting'''.}}\n# to [[expect]]\n#: {{ux|fr|On '''attendait''' mieux de toi.|We '''expected''' better from you.}}\n# {{lb|fr|reflexive}} to [[expect]] {{+obj|fr|:à}}\n#: {{uxi|fr|Je m''''attendais''' à pire.|I '''expected''' worse.}}\n#: {{ux|fr|Il s''''attend''' à ce que tu viennes ce soir.|He '''expects''' you to come tonight.}}\n#: {{ux|fr|Pourquoi est-ce que je me suis '''attendu''' à ce que vous ayez la gentillesse de me laisser tranquille ?|Why did I '''expect''' you to be nice enough to leave me in peace?}}\n#* {{quote-book|fr|title=Trois mois de campagne au Maroc : étude géographique de la région parcourue|author={{w|Frédéric Weisgerber}}|year=1904|location=Paris|publisher=Ernest Leroux|page=38|text=Notre hôte, absent au moment de notre arrivée, ne tarde pas à paraître et me fait l’accueil auquel je m''''attendais''' de sa part.|t=Our host, absent at the time of our arrival, did not take long to appear and gave me the welcome which I '''expected''' of him.}}\n# {{lb|fr|Louisiana French}} {{alternative form of|fr|entendre}}, to [[hear]]\n#: {{ux|fr|Quand t'étais petit, t''''attendais''' le français à la Messe ou a l'église?|When you were little, would you '''hear''' French at Mass or at church?}}\n\n====Usage notes====\n* A [[false friend]] of {{m+|en|attend}}, of which meanings to do with waiting are archaic.\n\n====Conjugation====\n{{fr-conj-auto}}\n\n====Derived terms====\n{{col3|fr\n|attendre au tournant\n|attendre cent sept ans\n|attendre comme le Messie\n|attendre famille\n|attendre son heure\n|attendre un heureux événement\n|attendu que\n|ne perdre rien pour attendre\n|tout vient à point à qui sait attendre}}\n\n","alt":["entendre"],"syn":[],"type":"verb","forms":[{"mod":"inf","aux":["avoir"],"pronom":true,"impers":false}],"trans":["to wait","to wait for, to await","to expect","to expect .mw-parser-output .object-usage-tag{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output .deprecated{color:olivedrab}","alternative form of entendre, to hear"],"group":3,"conj":[{"mod":"indc","tenses":[{"tense":"pres","forms":[["j'attend","s"],["tu attend","s"],["il attend",""],["nous attend","ons"],["vous attend","ez"],["ils attend","ent"]]},{"tense":"pass-c","forms":[["j'ai attend","u"],["tu as attend","u"],["il a attend","u"],["nous avons attend","u"],["vous avez attend","u"],["ils ont attend","u"]]},{"tense":"impf","forms":[["j'attend","ais"],["tu attend","ais"],["il attend","ait"],["nous attend","ions"],["vous attend","iez"],["ils attend","aient"]]},{"tense":"pqpf","forms":[["j'avais attend","u"],["tu avais attend","u"],["il avait attend","u"],["nous avions attend","u"],["vous aviez attend","u"],["ils avaient attend","u"]]},{"tense":"pass-s","forms":[["j'attend","is"],["tu attend","is"],["il attend","it"],["nous attend","îmes"],["vous attend","îtes"],["ils attend","irent"]]},{"tense":"pass-a","forms":[["j'eus attend","u"],["tu eus attend","u"],["il eut attend","u"],["nous eûmes attend","u"],["vous eûtes attend","u"],["ils eurent attend","u"]]},{"tense":"futr","forms":[["j'attend","rai"],["tu attend","ras"],["il attend","ra"],["nous attend","rons"],["vous attend","rez"],["ils attend","ront"]]},{"tense":"futr-a","forms":[["j'